attachments.title: Grinny Grandad - Monty - **FREE DL** by Freshly Squeezed (Record Label)
attachments.text:
Download the full EP for FREE: 

'Monty' - Track 1 from Grinny Grandad's 'The Car Boot-Leg EP'.

Grinny Grandad is a York based music collective whose songs have appeared in Grand Theft Auto (San Andreas and Liberty City Stories), Desperados Beer Advert and various TV shows – Come Dine With Me, Super Scrimpers (Channel 4), The One Show (BBC 1), Celebrity Wedding Planner (Channel 5). Their music can also be heard on the soundtrack of French film La Croisiere. Grinny Grandad has received radio support from BBC Radio (BBC Radio 1, BBC Radio 2, BBC Radio 6), XFM and Kiss FM as well as a live session at the infamous Maida Vale Studios for BBC Radio 1. Regularly playing festivals including Glastonbury and hold a residency at Beatherder. 

“I’ve not heard drums played with such power and feeling since Jon Bonham of Led Zeppelin.” 
- Tom Robinson, BBC 6 music 

‘Riding the beats are soul-driven vocals which should provide all five of your five a day’ - MixMag 

‘Shot of sunshine' - Data Transmission 

‘Feel good funk’ – Fame Magazine

--------

Follow Freshly Squeezed for more great music!
